summary:
I am a Canadian-born basketball player currently pursuing a professional career in Europe. I am a former player for the Brampton Honey Badgers (CEBL) and Aris Leeuwarden (BNXT). This summer I signed with the Antwerp Giants of the BNXT League for the 2023-24 season.

Graduate of Dalhousie University (‘22) with a Bachelor in Commerce and Entrepreneurship.

Passionate about youth sport and giving back to the next generation of athletes!
